summaryText:
**One-line Description:**
Firm-fixed price service contract for auditing Aerospace AS9100D / AS9110C Standards at Letterkenny Army Depot in Chambersburg, Pennsylvania.

**Summary Paragraph:**
Letterkenny Army Depot is seeking a contractor to perform an audit to sustain certification for the Aerospace AS9100D / AS9110C Standards. This contract will include a twelve-month base period and four twelve-month option years. Although the exact value of the contract is not specified, the work will be conducted under NAICS code 541611 with a size standard of $24.5 million. The work will be performed on-site at Letterkenny Army Depot, Chambersburg, PA. The project, tagged under federal solicitation number W911N2-25-Q-0023, will be released for bidding on April 22, 2025, with proposals due by May 7, 2025. This contract will involve expertise in areas such as auditing, consulting, and possibly other aspects of administrative and general management consulting to ensure compliance with specified aerospace standards. The number of people required for the project has not been specified. Interested contractors must be registered in the SAM database to be eligible for the award.
